@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Create a cash transaction (inpayment)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "a1b2c3d4-0001-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "datetime": "2026-01-10T09:00:00Z",
  "date": "2026-01-10",
  "accountType": "DEFAULT",
  "category": "CASH",
  "type": "CUSTOMER_INPAYMENT",
  "amount": 2500.00,
  "fee": null,
  "tax": null,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "description": "Monthly salary"
}

###

### Create a card transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "a1b2c3d4-0002-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "datetime": "2026-01-15T14:30:00Z",
  "date": "2026-01-15",
  "accountType": "DEFAULT",
  "category": "CASH",
  "type": "CARD_TRANSACTION",
  "amount": 42.80,
  "fee": null,
  "tax": null,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "description": "Grocery shopping",
  "merchantName": "REWE",
  "mccCode": "5411"
}

###

### Create a BUY trade
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "a1b2c3d4-0003-0000-0000-000000000003",
  "datetime": "2026-02-01T10:15:00Z",
  "date": "2026-02-01",
  "accountType": "DEFAULT",
  "category": "TRADING",
  "type": "BUY",
  "amount": 500.00,
  "fee": 1.00,
  "tax": null,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "description": "Buy AAPL",
  "assetSymbol": "AAPL",
  "assetName": "Apple Inc.",
  "assetClass": "STOCK",
  "shares": 3.0,
  "price": 166.67
}

###

### Create an international card transaction with FX info
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "a1b2c3d4-0004-0000-0000-000000000004",
  "datetime": "2026-03-05T18:00:00Z",
  "date": "2026-03-05",
  "accountType": "DEFAULT",
  "category": "CASH",
  "type": "CARD_TRANSACTION_INTERNATIONAL",
  "amount": 28.50,
  "fee": 0.50,
  "tax": null,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "description": "Restaurant in London",
  "merchantName": "Dishoom",
  "mccCode": "5812",
  "fxOriginalAmount": 24.00,
  "fxOriginalCurrency": "GBP",
  "fxRate": 1.1875
}

###

### Get all transactions (default page size 50)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions

###

### Get all transactions — page 2, size 10, sorted by date descending
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions?page=1&size=10&sort=date,desc

###

### Get transaction by UUID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/a1b2c3d4-0001-0000-0000-000000000001

###

### Get transactions by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/by-category/CASH

###

### Get transactions by category — TRADING
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/by-category/TRADING

###

### Get transactions by type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/by-type/CARD_TRANSACTION

###

### Get transactions by type — BUY
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/by-type/BUY

###

### Get transactions by MCC code
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/by-mcc/5411

###

### Get transactions by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/by-date?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-03-31

###

### Import transactions from CSV
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/import/csv
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="transactions.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ../example.csv
--boundary--

###

### Import Sparkasse transactions from JSON export
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/import/sparkasse-json
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sparkasse.json"
Content-Type: application/json

< ../sparkasse_example.json
--boundary--

###

### Search transactions by merchant name (cross-source: TR + Sparkasse)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/by-merchant?q=McDonalds

###

### Merchant search — paginated + sorted
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/by-merchant?q=billa&page=0&size=20&sort=date,desc
